			Ok I wrote about this wep earlier.....<BR>
<BR>
Like I said I was VERY fortunate and got this at lev 16. I am lev 28 now and still use it, but only because I just dont have anythign to replace it with. AT lev 21 I started realizing this wep was too slow and didnt do enough damage, however I still like the effect. On the flip side of that is the effect will either dispell or not hold if you have any other sort of buff on.<BR>
<BR>
Ive seen it sell for around 200PP... Id say its worth it, but its hard for the levs should use this to generate that kinda cash (15-20?)<BR>
<BR>
Now in search of a better wep.... most likely gonna be a runed falchon. My buds and I are going to go camp it soon (I'm the low man on the totem pole...oh well) Also its hard to find a decent ranger wep. (Im not a big fan of axes and/or claws, nothing personal I know EVERYONE out there likes the thulian claw but appearance wise I think a cool sword looks much better. However if you could wear both the claw and carry a wep that would be bad@$$.)<BR>
